Londen Jan Kent & comp
on the 21 past remitted you £710: - N13 seconds bills
indorsed £460 on the carle of Ranelagh & £120 &
£130: ons dewaerd stringer, of which the first accepted
in your handes, inlosed 4 bills more viz £100 & £110:-
on Sr. Joseph Herne & £150 on John du maistre & £100
on Anthony marry for all which procure the needfull &
advise mee, now have yours of 5 & 12 past godsend the
Rott convoy wel over butt all rivers beeng frosen will
detaine that pack bill open water as well as N 29 aboard van
swol who lyes frosen between ostend & bridges & I have
send people theter in hope to gett my pack out, butt ofber
theij have putt. att least ⅓ of the loading above deck
could not find itt, soo itt must be on the bottem the
stranded good are much damaged I would have you
ship alwayes in old knowne, seaman, boath
for ostend & other places, for those by ostend
stranded by their negligence, & the vessels that are
att hom att ostend & strangers kept itt there &
under way, butt these that lives att bridges yett
home & so an other have their goods, I have yo
remise of £200 on Robert mitlow I shall procure
the needfull, buy no pack whites yett: I have some
thoughts to order some monneyes in london to be given
upon the lives of my 3 sames att 14 p c p ant
pray give mee yor advise & opinion there of some are
much against itt here, & others hold itto for vere goods
award pray & how long wee can come in yett I exspect
the kerss: & one pack of cloth by this convoy for amst
att hull & advise what passes rest
so

In antwoort aende ue van 14 & 29 paso inden vercoop van ue reste
aende pyelakens is niets gepasseert, & nu geen hopes over die voor
aenstaende naersomer te vercoopen, hebbende middelertijt ue trats
van ƒ202 wisselgelt voor nicolaes de rousseau voldaen
wenschte wel in iedts profitabelder ue conde dienen terwijl
beuven
Amst Rover
In antwoort aende ue van 21 past & p deser, wy syn tot Rott
aende quaede syde, myne 5 lakens sijn daer geheel bevonden & hebbe
die oock doen incoopen, hoe dat werck op anelant is toegegaen
is mij geheel vremt want van die is noch ½, nochte 10 pp gecort
t gene tot ostende inde laeste gestrande schepen is gesalveert, is
aen een ieder overgelevert & hebbe ick mijn pack geheel & al
becomen, on dertusschen wat oncosten ue gedaen gelieft mij die
belaeten weten & aen mons pradellis de sijne oock voldoen
sal mijn rembourso dan hier vinden den wisselbrief van
£100 tot laste S Jan & Franc Eyles is met protest aen
